  <main id="top">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="gridlines"></div>
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="eyebrow">Strategic CFO Leadership</div>
        <h1>Fractional CFO services in California and San Diego.</h1>
        <p>Fractional CFO and outsourced CFO leadership for growth companies in California, San Diego, Mexico and the United States: control cash flow, improve margins, structure capital and make sharper decisions.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions"><a class="btn gold" href="#contact">Start the Roadmap</a><a class="btn" href="#services">Explore Services →</a></div>
      </div>
      <aside class="hero-card">
        <div class="label">Finance diagnostic readiness</div>
        <strong>30-day stabilization sprint</strong>
        <p style="color:#bbb;line-height:1.6;margin:0">Cash discipline, KPI visibility, FP&A reporting, cost control, margin focus and board-level decision support.</p>
        <div class="meter"><span></span></div>
        <small style="color:#999">Designed for CEOs, owners and private equity-backed growth companies in California, San Diego and Mexico.</small>
      </aside>
    </section>

      <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat"><b>30+</b><span>Years CFO Experience</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><b>$1B+</b><span>Assets Managed</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><b>$250M+</b><span>M&A Transactions</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><b>4</b><span>Markets Served: California, San Diego, Mexico, LatAm</span></div>
    </div>

    <section id="services" class="light">
      <div class="section-head"><div><div class="eyebrow">What we do</div><h2>Core CFO Services in California, San Diego and Mexico</h2></div><p>From cash flow management to strategic finance consulting, FINIDI acts as the financial command center your business needs to grow with discipline across California, San Diego, Mexico and the United States.</p></div>
      <div class="cards">
        <article class="service"><div class="icon">⌖</div><h3>Financial Strategy Consulting in San Diego</h3><ul><li>Strategic planning and execution for California growth companies</li><li>Profitability analysis</li><li>Board-level CFO guidance</li><li>Trusted advisor to leadership</li></ul><a class="learn">Learn more →</a></article>
        <article class="service"><div class="icon">▥</div><h3>Cash Flow Management in California</h3><ul><li>52-week cash forecast</li><li>Working capital strategy for San Diego and Mexico operations</li><li>Treasury oversight</li><li>Cost and cash utilization</li></ul><a class="learn">Learn more →</a></article>
        <article class="service"><div class="icon">↗</div><h3>Growth & M&A Support for San Diego Companies</h3><ul><li>Budgeting and rolling forecast</li><li>M&A financial support</li><li>Project finance modeling</li><li>Process improvements across California, Mexico and LatAm</li></ul><a class="learn">Learn more →</a></article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="split">
      <div class="bio">
        <div class="eyebrow">Who we are</div>
        <h2>A senior fractional CFO partner you can rely on.</h2>
        <p>Alejandro Payró brings 30+ years of finance leadership across banking, consulting, logistics, tourism, retail, mining, manufacturing and private equity-backed companies.</p>
        <p>He has led finance teams across the USA, California, San Diego, Mexico and LatAm, supported accelerated-growth businesses, managed board and audit committee reporting, and executed major capital and M&A initiatives including a US$1.5B debt issuance and a US$250M acquisition.</p>
        <p>FINIDI turns that operator-level experience into practical CFO consulting services for California, San Diego, Mexico and LatAm: cash discipline, stronger reporting, sharper planning and financial decisions that CEOs and owners can act on.</p>
        <div class="creds"><div class="cred"><b>Electrical Mechanical Engineer</b><span>Universidad Panamericana</span></div><div class="cred"><b>MBA</b><span>Kellogg School of Management</span></div><div class="cred"><b>Private Equity</b><span>$1B+ fund management exposure</span></div><div class="cred"><b>Board Experience</b><span>Independent director and audit committee chair</span></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="portrait"><img src="/Foto%20APO.png" alt="Alejandro Payró, fractional CFO for California, San Diego and Mexico" width="1215" height="1282" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
    </section>

    <section id="pricing" class="dark">
      <div class="section-head"><div><div class="eyebrow">Engagement models</div><h2>Fractional CFO Pricing for California and San Diego</h2></div><p style="color:#aaa">Choose the leadership intensity your company needs: focused part-time CFO support, broad CFO coverage or near full-time strategic integration for California, San Diego, Mexico or cross-border operations.</p></div>
      <div class="pricing">
        <article class="price"><h3>Starter CFO Support</h3><div class="amount">$7,000 <small>/ month</small></div><ul><li>Average 10 hours per week</li><li>Two half-days engagement</li><li>Focused CFO areas</li><li>Remote support for California and San Diego companies</li></ul><a class="btn" href="#contact">Get Started</a></article>
        <article class="price featured"><div class="badge">Most Popular</div><h3>Growth CFO Support</h3><div class="amount">$13,000 <small>/ month</small></div><ul><li>Average 20+ hours per week</li><li>Daily engagement flexibility</li><li>Scheduled on-site availability in Mexico and cross-border support</li><li>Comprehensive CFO coverage for San Diego growth companies</li></ul><a class="btn gold" href="#contact">Get Started</a></article>
        <article class="price"><h3>Strategic CFO Support</h3><div class="amount">$18,000 <small>/ month</small></div><ul><li>Average 30+ hours per week</li><li>Daily availability</li><li>Full integration as team member</li><li>Board-level partnership for California, San Diego and Mexico operations</li></ul><a class="btn" href="#contact">Get Started</a></article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="process" class="light">
      <div class="section-head"><div><div class="eyebrow">How it starts</div><h2>CFO Roadmap Process for San Diego and California</h2></div><p>Fast onboarding, immediate financial planning visibility and a practical execution plan built with your existing team and systems in California, San Diego, Mexico or the United States.</p></div>
      <div class="process">
        <div class="step"><em>01</em><h3>California Kick Off</h3><p>Leadership alignment, priorities, pain points and immediate cash visibility.</p></div>
